<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>2026-05 on</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/tags/2026-05/</link><description>Recent content in 2026-05 on</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 26 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://yshghid.github.io/tags/2026-05/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>CNN #1 RNA interference 효율 예측 모델</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/study/dl/dl61/</link><pubDate>Tue, 26 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/study/dl/dl61/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="cnn-1-rna-interference-효율-예측-모델"&gt;
 CNN #1 RNA interference 효율 예측 모델
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#cnn-1-rna-interference-%ed%9a%a8%ec%9c%a8-%ec%98%88%ec%b8%a1-%eb%aa%a8%eb%8d%b8"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;#2026-02-27&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id="개요"&gt;
 개요
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#%ea%b0%9c%ec%9a%94"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;siRNA 서열을 입력받아서 RNA interference 효율을 예측하는 회귀 모델&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;siRNA 길이: 21bp&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;위치당 염기 종류: 4&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;-&amp;gt; input shape: (21,4)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id=""&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;모델 구조&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;features &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; tf&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;keras&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;Input(shape&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;21&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;))
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;prev &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; features
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; i &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; range(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;):
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; prev &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; layers&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;Conv1D(
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; filters&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; kernel_size&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; activation&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;tf&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;nn&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;relu,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; padding&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;same&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; )(prev)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; prev &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; layers&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;Dropout(rate&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0.3&lt;/span&gt;)(prev)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;output &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; layers&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;Dense(
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; units&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; activation&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;tf&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;math&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;sigmoid
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;)(layers&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;Flatten()(prev))
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;keras_model &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; tf&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;keras&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;Model(inputs&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;features, outputs&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;output)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;keras_model&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;summary()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;21bp siRNA sequence를 입력받고&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;두 개의 Conv1D layer로 RNAi 효율 관련 염기 패턴을 학습하고&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;0~1 사이의 효율값을 예측.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;요약하면 이렇다.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>env #3 venv 초기 설정법</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/study/be/be61/</link><pubDate>Tue, 26 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/study/be/be61/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="env-3-venv-초기-설정법"&gt;
 env #3 venv 초기 설정법
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#env-3-venv-%ec%b4%88%ea%b8%b0-%ec%84%a4%ec%a0%95%eb%b2%95"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;#2026-05-26&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# 1. 가상환경 생성&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;python3.11 -m venv .venv
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# 2. 활성화&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;source .venv/bin/activate
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# 3. pip 업그레이드&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;pip install --upgrade pip
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# 4. 패키지 설치&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;pip install -r requirements.txt
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# 5. typing_extensions 업그레이드 (IPython 호환성)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;pip install &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;typing_extensions&amp;gt;=4.6.0&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; --upgrade
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# 6. Jupyter kernel 등록&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;python -m ipykernel install --user --name workspace --display-name &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Python (workspace)&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# 7. 노트북 실행&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;jupyter lab
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>평범한하루</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/hobby/daily/daily61/</link><pubDate>Tue, 26 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/hobby/daily/daily61/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="특별한하루"&gt;
 특별한하루
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#%ed%8a%b9%eb%b3%84%ed%95%9c%ed%95%98%eb%a3%a8"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;#2026-05-26&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;img width="3360" height="2100" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/c915aefd-bf3d-4548-a35c-704cca447f55" /&gt;
&lt;img width="1262" height="1684" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/b6b171ab-6aba-4d7a-aad6-3cdf61fc342d" /&gt;
&lt;img width="1264" height="1686" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/a7d91008-cf20-4e56-829a-e23dc8771727" /&gt;
&lt;img width="3360" height="2100" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/09a28cf9-1db9-4a99-94bc-ff2f3cd07ae7" /&gt;
&lt;img width="3360" height="2100" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/caf39887-6cd5-4e62-a3ee-19033a736a6b" /&gt;
&lt;img width="2160" height="2880" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/36111d44-5dbd-4e8b-b412-8a39bb56162e" /&gt;</description></item><item><title>여름 맨날맨날템 모음 + 최근에 산것</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/hobby/daily/daily60/</link><pubDate>Fri, 22 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/hobby/daily/daily60/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="여름-맨날맨날템-모음--최근에-산것"&gt;
 여름 맨날맨날템 모음 + 최근에 산것
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#%ec%97%ac%eb%a6%84-%eb%a7%a8%eb%82%a0%eb%a7%a8%eb%82%a0%ed%85%9c-%eb%aa%a8%ec%9d%8c--%ec%b5%9c%ea%b7%bc%ec%97%90-%ec%82%b0%ea%b2%83"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;#2026-05-22&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;일단 최근에 산것부터 나열 !!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="776" height="956" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/0a036abe-76e0-49c8-aaaf-180f001c2fea" /&gt;
&lt;img width="778" height="956" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/7d8b9368-4756-40fb-a23b-6f651f1ceaba" /&gt;
&lt;img width="776" height="952" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/bbd2d3df-f86c-4c15-921e-b4f1cf3a2ad3" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;흑청 데님이랑 입으면 댈것같아서 코닥 반팔티를 샀구 비바셔스에서 부츠컷 데님을 샀다. 사이즈 고민을 좀 했는데 허리/힙/허벅지/밑위/밑단 순으로
S는 33/44/24.5/27/23.5, M은 35/46/25.5/28/24.5, L은 37/48/27/28.5/25.5였는데, 원래같으면 S를 사서 스키니 느낌으로 입었을것같은데 최근에 살이 마니 찌기도 했구
약간 덜 붙는 느낌이 드는게 낫나? 해서 M을 샀다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;첨엔 L을 골라서 결제까지 했는데(이유: 허벅지단면/밑단단면이 갠찮음) 허리가 넘 클것같아서 그냥 M으로 했다. 사실 핏이 잘 상상이 안가서 걱정+고민+기대가 댄다..!&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>5월 2주(5.11-5.15)</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/study/ncc/ncc3/</link><pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/study/ncc/ncc3/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="5월-2주511-515"&gt;
 5월 2주(5.11-5.15)
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#5%ec%9b%94-2%ec%a3%bc511-515"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;#2026-05-12&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;이번주 할일&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;11일 월요일 오후 3시 미팅 (zoom)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;13일 수요일 오후 4시 미팅 (zoom)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;14일 목요일 오전 9시 주간회의 (검진동 6층 회의실) / 오후 2시 20분 면담 (검진동 7층 탕비실)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;15일 오전 10시 FMI 인수인계 / 오후 2시 KPMNG 정기미팅 (그랜드 인터컨티넨탈 서울 파르나스)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;이번주 메모&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;15일 출장 다녀오면 김송이 선생님께 복무신청서랑 출장보고서 제출 (양식 보내주셨음)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;다음주에 WGS 전달 일정 문의하기 (이노크라스)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;KPMNG 정기미팅 참석 메일 - &lt;a href="https://yshghid.github.io/ncc/data/0507.pdf"&gt;0507.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;27일 수요일 오후3시 암빅데이터센터 월간회의 (검진동 5층 회의실)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;27일 수요일 오후1시10분 CGDB 위원 미팅&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id=""&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h2 id="511"&gt;
 5.11
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#511"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;업무내용&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>5월 3주(5.18-5.22)</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/study/ncc/ncc5/</link><pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/study/ncc/ncc5/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="5월-3주518-522"&gt;
 5월 3주(5.18-5.22)
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#5%ec%9b%94-3%ec%a3%bc518-522"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;#2026-05-18&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;이번주 할일&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;6월 WGS 전달 일정 문의하기 (이노크라스)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;20일 수요일 오후 4시 CGDB 미팅 (Zoom)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;이번주 메모&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;6월 KOSMOS 월간회의 일정 조사&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;27일 수요일 오후1시10분 CGDB 위원 미팅&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;27일 수요일 오후3시 암빅데이터센터 월간회의 (검진동 5층 회의실)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id=""&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h2 id="518"&gt;
 5.18
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#518"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;오늘할일&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;MAF-Report 매칭 작업&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;매칭작업 월간회의 자료 작성하기&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;KOSMOS 월간회의 일정조사 리마인드 메일보내기&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;MAF-Report 매칭 작업&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;공유 ppt - &lt;a href="https://yshghid.github.io/ncc/data/0518.pdf"&gt;0518.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;월간회의 첨부자료 작성&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;월간회의 첨부자료 - &lt;a href="https://yshghid.github.io/ncc/data/0518-2.pdf"&gt;0518-2.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id=""&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h2 id="519"&gt;
 5.19
